---

<PageLayout
  title="About Me"
  description="Senior Software Engineer based in Hyderabad, India - working across the full stack with TypeScript, React, Node.js, and AWS."
>
  <!-- Bio -->
  <div
    class="prose prose-lg prose-invert text-zinc-100 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl"
  >
    <h1
      class="text-4xl sm:text-[2.75rem] font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-8 font-outfit"
    >
      About Me
    </h1>

    <p>
      Hi, I'm Savitha &#128075;&#127995;! Welcome to my little corner of the
      internet.
    </p>

    <p>
      I currently work as a <strong class="text-white"
        >Senior Software Engineer</strong
      >, building full-stack web applications and internal developer tooling. My
      stack of choice is
      <strong class="text-white"
        >TypeScript, React, Next.js, Node.js, GraphQL, and AWS</strong
      >. I'm currently deepening my expertise in distributed systems, system
      design, and AI/GenAI tooling.
    </p>

    <p>
      Outside work, I write about things I learn - distributed systems patterns,
      frontend architecture, and the occasional deep dive into something I found
      genuinely interesting. I also maintain reading notes on papers and
      engineering blogs that shape how I think.
    </p>

    <p>
      When I'm not at a keyboard, I'm out with my camera &#128248;, reading
      philosophy &#128218;, listening to music &#127925;, working out 🏋️‍♀️, or
      doing yoga 🧘‍♀️. I'm also a nature enthusiast &#127807; who loves spending
      time outdoors.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you want to talk tech, swap ideas, or have an opportunity worth
      discussing - reach out via <a
        href="mailto:gsavitha@protonmail.com?subject=Hello"
        class="text-primary hover:text-primary-hover">email</a
      > or <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/g-savitha/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-primary hover:text-primary-hover">LinkedIn</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>

  <hr class="border-zinc-700/50 my-16" />

  <!-- Experience -->
